            <abstract>
                <p>A miniature with four episodes, showing: first, the Caliph ordering his troops to
                    destroy a Church in ʾAtrib; second, <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> appearing to the
                    Caliph (who was asleep) to order his agent to stop the destruction of the
                    Church with a white dove appearing to take his letter between them; third, the
                    dove giving the letter written by the caliph to the head of troops (agent of
                    the Caliph) with the Abbot of the Church standing in the gate, and
                    fourth, the Caliph who later become believer sitting in front of the Church.</p>

            </abstract>
